703167f-a.folder: Bedford Avenue & Sullivan Place, Brooklyn, NY

706924f-a.text:
Sullivan Place, west from Bedford Ave. A view of Ehbets Eield, the baseball grounds of the Brooklyn Dodgers. Pine Place once ran through the center of the groundS.  The Clove Road or "old Road to Bedford" ran the
whole width of the south side of the grounds.
June 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
